==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Chare
<hw>Chare</hw>, }</mhw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To
work by the day, without being a regularly hired servant; to do small
jobs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Char</ent>⟦br⟧

