HEADWORD: Chare
<hw>Chare</hw> <pr>(ch⟦acir⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A narrow
street.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

